OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1774451489
OL,3,CEmergency gas price rise across
OL,4,CChannel Islands as stark warning issued
OL,6,FAn emergency gas price rise has been
OL,7,Fannounced across the Channel Islands
OL,8,Fdue to the impact of the Iran War.
OL,10,FAll tariffs will increase by 1.2p per
OL,11,Fkilowatt-hour from Tuesday 7 April -
OL,12,Fmeaning households on the most
OL,13,Fpopular, standard tariff will pay an
OL,14,Fextra 5%.
OL,16,FIsland Energy says businesses will
OL,17,Falso face higher bills, but the extent
OL,18,Fof price rises will depend on their
OL,19,Findividual circumstances.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
