PN,38402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1774451489
OL,3,CEmergency gas price rise across
OL,4,CChannel Islands as stark warning issued
OL,6,FAll customers are being written to by
OL,7,Fthe company, which says there will be
OL,8,Fworse to come if the conflict in the
OL,9,FMiddle East continues to see wholesale
OL,10,Ffees spike.
OL,12,FIt adds: "The ongoing situation in the
OL,13,FStrait of Hormuz and the attacks on
OL,14,Fgas facilities in the region have
OL,15,Fcaused the price to rise dramatically."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
