OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1774451489
OL,3,CEmergency gas price rise across
OL,4,CChannel Islands as stark warning issued
OL,6,FGraeme Millar, Chief Executive Officer
OL,7,Fof the Islands Energy Group, explains:
OL,8,F"The conflict-related volatility has
OL,9,Fcaused a steep rise in the wholesale
OL,10,Fcost of gas and is a direct pass-
OL,11,Fthrough of the amount we are now
OL,12,Fpaying to secure supply.
OL,14,F"We want to reassure our customers
OL,15,Fthat Island Energy is not making
OL,16,Fadditional profit from this temporary
OL,17,Fadjustment.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1774451489
OL,3,CEmergency gas price rise across
OL,4,CChannel Islands as stark warning issued
OL,6,F"Our hedging strategy - where we buy
OL,7,Ffuture volumes at pre-agreed prices -
OL,8,Fhas helped to limit the extent of this
OL,9,Fincrease and shield customers from
OL,10,Feven greater instability.
OL,12,F"However, it is important to be clear
OL,13,Fand transparent. If wholesale prices
OL,14,Fremain elevated as our hedged
OL,15,Fcontracts expire, further price
OL,16,Fincreases will be necessary.
OL,18,F"The reality is that reductions can
OL,19,Fonly be considered when wholesale
OL,20,Frates fall back toward pre-conflict
OL,21,Flevels.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1774451489
OL,3,CEmergency gas price rise across
OL,4,CChannel Islands as stark warning issued
OL,6,F"Only when sustained and genuine cost
OL,7,Fdecreases occur can we safely reduce
OL,8,Ftariffs without risking instability in
OL,9,Fthe future."
OL,11,FIn response, both island governments
OL,12,Fsay their supply is resilient, with
OL,13,Fthe suggestion of financial support
OL,14,Ffrom Jersey authorities if the
OL,15,Fsituation does get worse.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1774451489
OL,3,CEmergency gas price rise across
OL,4,CChannel Islands as stark warning issued
OL,6,FChief Minister, Deputy Lyndon Farnham,
OL,7,Fexplains: "I just want to reassure
OL,8,Fislanders we're looking at how we
OL,9,Fmight be able to help if that
OL,10,Fincreases significantly and our supply
OL,11,Fchains are stable."
OL,13,FMeanwhile, Deputy Adrian Gabriel,
OL,14,FPresident of Guernsey's Environment
OL,15,Fand Infrastructure Committee, which is
OL,16,Fresponsible for supply chain security,
OL,17,Fsays: "I want to pass on that
OL,18,Freassurance that while costs are
OL,19,Fspiking, the supply to the island of
OL,20,Ffuels is not in question.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
